            en="Per Lumi §4.1: 'Gold is absolutely overpowered in the early game.' Combined with hero ointments / buckets / training helmets, gold-using players are 2–3 days ahead of free players in early development. The advantage narrows mid-game but stays meaningful (NPC Trader for crop emergencies)."
